IN RE APPLICATION OF 6011 GREENWICH WINDPARK, L.L.C. 2017-1375 Supreme Court of Ohio. February 28, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On appellant's motion to supplement record. Motion denied. On appellee's motion to dismiss and intervening appellee's motion to dismiss. Motions granted in part and denied in part. Appellant's assignment of error No. 2 dismissed. All other assignments of error remain pending.

O'Donnell, J., dissents and would grant the motion to supplement the record and the motions to dismiss the cause.

Kennedy and Fischer, JJ., would grant the motion to supplement the record.
